title: #193 - Christina Pazsitzky & ME
description: Stand up Comedian, Podcaster, "MTV-Road Rules" Alumni Christina Pazsitzky stop by the Mancave to have a VERY real conversation about depression, my drinking, the fat shaming campaign going on between me & her very FAT husband Tom Segura...then my wife joins in to mention what a horrible husband I am.
